text: Rachel Elise Blanchard (born March 19, 1976) is a Canadian actress. She played Hannah in the 2001 movie Sugar & Spice. She also played Maureen in the 2005 erotic movie Where the Truth Lies. Blanchard was born in Toronto, Ontario. ==References== == Other websites == * Category:Actors from Toronto Category:Canadian movie actors Category:Canadian television actors Category:1976 births Category:Living people
